之認定標準，請說明之。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:32:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0bbd4b387ee3", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114080", "c": "204", "s": "0817", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "人口政策與人口統計", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "戶政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-c5fb3965-moex-00004', 'heelevel3-c5fb3965', 'heelevel3-c5fb3965-moex-114-61b9f3c6', 'sub-heelevel3-c5fb3965-01', NULL, 'essay', '我們常用「人口加倍時間」以反映一個人口的成長速度和潛在人口課題。
